INFORMATION: [2020-02-07 07:22:47] Executed DbCommand (24ms) [Parameters=[@__user_Id_0='?' (Size = 450), @__edition_EditionId_1='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]

            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]

            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)

    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [PurchasedEditions] AS [p]
        WHERE (CASE
            WHEN ([p].[UserId] = @__user_Id_0) AND [p].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END & CASE
            WHEN ([p].[EditionId] = @__edition_EditionId_1) AND [p].[EditionId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
            ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
        END) = CAST(1 AS bit)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
